---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { prototypes } from "../data/site";
---

<BaseLayout title="产品原型 | WangAo-0" description="WangAo-0 的产品原型和 agent 平台构想。">
  <section class="page-shell">
    <div class="page-heading wide-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Product Prototypes</p>
      <h1>产品原型</h1>
      <p>这里不是灵感清单，而是把长期值得做的方向拆成可验证、可复盘、可逐步实现的产品假设。每个原型都先说明目标，再沉淀能力边界。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prototype-grid refined-prototypes">
      {prototypes.map((prototype) => (
        <article class="card prototype-card">
          <div class="prototype-card-head">
            <p class="card-kicker">{prototype.category}</p>
            <span class="status-pill">概念验证</span>
          </div>
          <h3>{prototype.title}</h3>
          <p>{prototype.description}</p>
          <div class="prototype-brief">
            <strong>核心能力</strong>
            <ul class="scope-list">
              {prototype.scope.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
